room_title: Escape room "Electrovault" by Countdown Louisville in Louisville
room_description: You and your friends are invited to Anika Tesla’s Manhattan penthouse for the birthday event of the season. Someone in your group uncovers her darkest secret and now you’re trapped on the 77th floor. You have one hour before the party turns into a 10,000-volt blowout, can you escape the ELECTROVAULT?
